stimulus:
Welcome to the Fasle Recall Experiment.

You will see and listen to 6 lists of 12-words one at a time. Try to remember as many as you can.

After the list, you’ll be asked to complete a recognition test.

Press any key to begin.

Now you will rate your confidence that each word occurred on the list.

Please indicate whether you think the word was definitely new, probably new, probably old, or definitely old.

Press any key to continue.
